  end], merge all overlapping intervals and return a new list of the non-
  overlapping intervals that cover all the intervals in the input.
  Example: Input: intervals = [[1,3],[2,6],[8,10],[15,18]]
  Output: [[1,6],[8,10],[15,18]] (Intervals [1,3] and [2,6] overlap, merging
  into [1,6])


